creator: OTP Bank Romania SA
descriptionHtml:
Here are just a few surprises waiting for you in the new SmartBank:

OTPcard biometrics - as cool as it sounds, as useful it is! With this functionality you can easily authorize the payments made online, with your card.

Treasury payments and foreign currency payments – the name says it all (we told you that the application is very intuitive 😄).

Share IBAN - because we know how often you need to send your current account number to others! From now on, it's very simple with the new SmartBank functionality!

Download the payment proof - there is no need to worry anymore, because the new version of the application comes with a quick download option.

For sure it will surprise you being more enjoyable to use SmartBank!

Don’t forget that the app is available in Romanian, English and Hungarian.
descriptionShort: With SmartBank you have banking at your disposal from anywhere at anytime!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Now with a modern design and new features, you will be surprised how friendly the new version of SmartBank is!

• a fresh, friendly, and intuitive look, with a focus on simplicity and accessibility;

• the ability to conceal your personal information, including account and deposit amounts;

See you in the SmartBank app!
